PrecisAppointment of J. DAVID HUNT of Selkirk, Manitoba, to be a Commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years; and his designation as Chief Commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission, effective May 1, 2024.
